\sphinxstylestrong{Projet\_JO} is a python project to sell tickets for the Olympic Games of Paris 2024. It\textquotesingle{}s student project, the tickets are not real.

\begin{sphinxadmonition}{note}{Note:}
\sphinxAtStartPar
This project is under active development.
\end{sphinxadmonition}
